{"tid":904442,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"打破在世藝術家最貴作品紀錄 霍克尼泳池肖像畫七億港元成交","createTime":"2018-11-16T10:49:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-16T15:42:55.000Z","uid":75969,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"e46bd46afa495546936eb118240ccfd78b4ee40a","tid":904442,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T10:49:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20181116/_2018111615053565300.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20181116%2F_2018111615053565300.jpg&h=11029d9f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n英國藝術家霍克尼（David Hockney）名作《藝術家肖像（泳池與兩個人像）》，周四由佳士得拍賣行在紐約拍賣，結果以9030萬美元（7.06億港元）成交，刷新在世藝術家作品的拍賣紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n這幅畫被譽為20世紀油畫代表作之一，去年曾參與在英國泰特現代美術館、法國龐畢度中心及美國大都會藝術博物館舉行巡迴展覽。<br />\n<br />\n這幅畫於1972年完成，顯示一名男子站在泳池邊觀看另一名男子游泳。佳士得戰後及當代藝術部門國際總監井上光司說，作品創作意念充滿趣味。霍克尼偶然把兩張無關的照片放在工作室地板，一幅是水底泳手，另一幅是凝視地下的男子，便決定合成一幅雙人肖像畫作。<br />\n<br />\n泳池是霍克尼心愛的主題，而池邊男子的靈感則來自作者的前戀人施萊辛格（Peter Schlesinger），他曾是霍克尼的模特兒，被視為霍克尼的愛人兼藝術創作的繆思，以他當模特兒，畫了很多在泳池旁的作品。但兩人於1971年分手。有指水底泳手其實是霍克尼的自畫像，在作品裡投射他當時心碎的情感。因為他當時已和施萊辛格分手。但亦有分析指水底泳手是施萊辛格的新戀人。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20181116/_2018111615053452823.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20181116%2F_2018111615053452823.jpg&h=caa857fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/866107\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F866107&d=sRrxY5Lmh0EsIZRmgEcxMY9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=02f11c00\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F866107&h=38539908\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/866107</a>"},{"pid":"f50b78791a7c4f98cba8e079b97a59e635958fb8","tid":904442,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T10:51:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8853b52f8a6836683ea276deb9f3d05c9a5aefe2","tid":904442,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T10:52:54.000Z","msg":"包埋條女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbdb33318884a87d09e06f2093e8c41171c767e6","tid":904442,"uid":191394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T10:53:30.000Z","msg":"hehe畫<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1e7b081067dfabb736444afbfd2e0f8f57eaa18","tid":904442,"uid":109133,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T10:56:31.000Z","msg":"又洗黑錢"},{"pid":"ca7f3795107d22b7c40451d49f1bfb0b71f74519","tid":904442,"uid":49197,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T10:58:11.000Z","msg":"垃圾"},{"pid":"4dc29b32973b253c1bd081c37c7c6f9d137fba0f","tid":904442,"uid":55458,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T10:58:33.000Z","msg":"藝術係一個騙局"},{"pid":"fdfe9ca1836a2ec67cebf6d45da98bf527264f8f","tid":904442,"uid":29138,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T11:11:13.000Z","msg":"有指<br />\n分析指<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e973625cf03ddf2896e39b5657304e3de57ce71","tid":904442,"uid":69221,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T12:01:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Dw5kme5Q_Yo&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DDw5kme5Q_Yo%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=sRrxY5Lmh0EsIZRmgEcxMY9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=7b2b0b62\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Dw5kme5Q_Yo&amp;feature=youtu.be</a><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"157134227540bf9f1d2